engineVersion.description: Version number of the Redis engine used by the cluster.

maintenanceWindow.description: The weekly time range during which maintenance on the cluster is performed.

nodeType.description: Compute and memory capacity of the nodes in the cluster.

numShards.description: Number of shards in the cluster.

parameterGroupName.description: Name of the parameter group associated with the cluster.

port.description: Port number on which the cluster accepts connections.

snapshotRetentionLimit.description: Number of days for which MemoryDB retains automatic snapshots before deleting them.

snapshotWindow.description: The daily time range (in UTC) during which MemoryDB begins taking a daily snapshot of the shard.

subnetGroupName.description: Name of the subnet group used by the cluster.

topicArn.description: ARN of the SNS topic to which cluster notifications are sent.

vpcId.description: The VPC in which the cluster exists.
